Facebook post, 7 December 2022. Text only: Ye Kalyug hai - koi nahi manega, na koi sunega. Bohat rare 5D Souls honge jinko kuch samh ayega. Aur unko khud bhagwan ne chunaa hoga. Translation: This is Kaliyug - very rare 5D Souls chosen by God will understand. Aspect: Energy Activation - only divinely chosen 5D Souls perceive the Parivartan.